quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  39,42,"God claims back every soul upon its death, and the souls of the living when they are asleep. Those that are doomed to die He keeps, and lets the others go for a time ordained. Surely in this there are signs for people that reflect"
  39,43,"Have they chosen others besides God to intercede for them? Say: ‘Even though they have no power nor understanding?‘"
  39,44,"Say: ‘Intercession is wholly in the hands of God. His is the sovereignty over the heavens and the earth. Then to Him shall you be recalled.‘"
  39,45,"When God alone is named, the hearts of those who deny the hereafter shrink with aversion; but when their other gods are named, they are filled with joy"
  39,46,"Say: ‘Lord, Creator of the heavens and the earth, who has knowledge of the unknown and the manifest, You alone can judge Your servants‘ differences.‘"
  39,47,"If the wrongdoers possessed all the treasures of the earth and as much besides, they would gladly offer it to redeem their souls from the harrowing scourge on the Day of Resurrection. For God will show them what they have never reckoned with"
  39,48,"And the evil of their deeds will manifest itself to them, and that which they derided will encompass them"
  39,49,"And when evil befalls man he calls out to Us; but when, instead, We vouchsafe him a favour from Ourself, he says: ‘It is my due.‘ By no means! It is but a test: yet most of them do not know it"
  39,50,"The same was said by those before them: but they gained nothing from what they did, and the very evil of their deeds recoiled upon them"
  39,51,"And the wrongdoers among these¹ shall also have the evil of their deeds recoil upon them: nor shall they ever be immune"
  39,52,Do they not know that God gives abundantly to whom He will and sparingly also? Surely in this there are signs for true believers